    "He took Hapvida public in April 2018 on the Sao Paulo stock exchange; his fortune now includes stakes held by his wife and his two sons.",
    "He is Hapvida's chairman; his son Jorge is the statutory chief executive officer, while his other son Candido Junior is a member of the board of directors.",
